      "content": "but if the programs are putting a strain on the economy by encouraging people to stay out of the workforce, isn't it less about \"systemic failure\" and more about the government actively creating a dependency culture? a lot of people feel like the current policy landscape is just making it harder for the economy to grow because the incentive to work is basically gone.",
